# Final Fix: POS Duplicate Invoice Prevention

This document contains only the final, working code changes required to completely prevent duplicate invoices from being generated via mouse double-clicks, keyboard shortcuts, or rapid form submissions on the POS screen.

## 1. Core Lock Implementation (`public/js/pos.js`)

**Target File:** `public/js/pos.js`

This change adds a "double-submit" protection lock directly into the AJAX form submission handlers.

### Change A: Main Checkout (`submitHandler`)
Find this line (around line 777):
```javascript
