```
**Change to:**
```javascript
var pos_is_submitting = false; // Add this global variable
pos_form_validator = pos_form_obj.validate({
```

Find the submission execution inside that block (around line 825):
```javascript
    if (cnf) {
        disable_pos_form_actions();

        var data = $(form).serialize();
//...
```
**Change to:**
```javascript
    if (cnf) {
        // --- ADD THIS LOCK BLOCK ---
